/**
 * Converts `value` to a finite number.
 *
 * @since 4.12.0
 * @category Lang
 * @param {*} value The value to convert.
 * @returns {number} Returns the converted number.
 * @example
 *
 * toFinite(3.2)
 * // => 3.2
 *
 * toFinite(Number.MIN_VALUE)
 * // => 5e-324
 *
 * toFinite(Infinity)
 * // => 1.7976931348623157e+308
 *
 * toFinite('3.2')
 * // => 3.2
 */Comment.Multiline
